\par \pard\plain \s17\sb0\sa120{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs24\lang2057
As Glaxosmithkline South Africa (Pty) Ltd is both\~  Applicant in the review as also the Appellant, I will, in the interests of simplicity, refer the company as Applicant.\~  Because the Act refers to the party against whom a complaint has been made regarding an alleged prohibited practice as the \'93respondent\'94, I will adopt that nomenclature when discussing the relevant provisions of the Act.\~  References to \'93respondent\'94 will be consistent with the wording of the Act.\~  References to the Respondents who are cited in the review and in the appeal will be made using an upper case first letter. }
