The Commission is empowered to refer the complaint to the Tribunal for adjudication at any time after the complaint is initiated (Section 50(1)).\~  However, the Commission must, within one year after the complaint was submitted to it, either refer the complaint to the Tribunal \'93if it determines that a prohibited practice has been established or in any other case, issue a notice of non-referral to the complainant in the prescribed form.\'94\~  (Section 50(2)).}
